text: Psiloteredo is a genus of ship-worms, marine bivalve molluscs of the family Teredinidae. == Species in the genus Psiloteredo == * Psiloteredo healdi (Bartsch, 1931) * Psiloteredo megotara (Hanley in Forbes & Hanley, 1848) * Psiloteredo senegalensis (Blainville, 1824) == References == Category:Molluscs described in 1922 Category:Teredinidae Category:Bivalve genera
title: Psiloteredo
